        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Devils are evil with a silver tongue, and one of your ancestors dallied in darkness or made an infernal pact.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> divine</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Deception, Religion</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Produce Flame]</em>, 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Charm]</em>, 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Floating Flame]{Flaming Sphere}</em>, 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Enthrall]</em>, 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Suggestion]</em>, 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wave of Despair]{Crushing Despair}</em>, 6th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Truesight]{True Seeing}</em>, 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Divine Decree]</em>, 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Divine Aura]</em>, 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Falling Stars]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Diabolic Edict]</em>, advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Embrace the Pit]</em>, greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Hellfire Plume]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> Hellfire scorches a target or fills your tongue with lies. Either a target takes 1 fire damage per spell level (if the spell already deals initial fire damage, combine this with the spell's initial damage before determining weaknesses and resistances), or you gain a +1 status bonus to Deception checks for 1 round.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Diabolic Blood Magic (Self)]</p>"
        },
